snippet.title: Virtual Mixer #32 - State Employees' Credit Union, Amber Fleming (Part 1 of 2)
snippet.description:
The Greater Mount Airy Chamber of Commerce held a Virtual Mixer on November 5, 2020. Guest Speaker, Amber Fleming, Senior Financial Services Advisor at State Employees' Credit Union shared details on how a credit union differs from a regular bank, services that they can provide, eligibility requirements, and a general update on how the organization is currently operating during the COVID-19 pandemic. We also briefly heard from SECU Senior Vice President, Lilnette Phillips. 

Part 2: https://youtu.be/qYbcQY2W4to

State Employees' Credit Union: https://www.ncsecu.org/
